msgid "Method used to repair the geometries. One of:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3214
msgid ""
"0 --- ``Linework``: combines all rings into a set of noded lines and then"
" extracts valid polygons from that linework"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3216
msgid ""
"1 --- ``Structure``: first makes all rings valid and then merges shells "
"and subtracts holes from shells to generate valid result. Assumes that "
"holes and shells are correctly categorized."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3220
msgid ""
"Using this method requires QGIS installed with GEOS_ >= 3.10 (see "
":menuselection:`Help --> About` menu)."
