#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6779
msgid "The maximum length of a line in the output."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6808
msgid ""
"The new line vector layer. The length of the feature geometries is less "
"than or equal to the length specified in the LENGTH parameter. An "
"additional field containing the ``order`` will be added."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6816
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:splitlinesbylength``"
